///    engine *evolve* and compose these basic blocks automatically into `sqrt(x) + 1`!
///
/// 2. Custom Operations Trait (Your Approach):
///    If your robot logic needs highly specialized operators that math doesn't cover 
///    (e.g., bitwise sensor shifts, specialized thresholds), you must build your own 
///    extensible trait-based tree rather than forcing it into Radiate's fixed math Enum.
